column1: 133025;instagram;2018-11-27 20:58:19;FALSE;"i've watched the qspiracy since the beginning.
steve bannon left the wh august last year and q appeared the following october. do you believe in coincidences?
abusing and leaking presidential information to mislead the people and benefit the hijacked party of puppets is obviously just business as usual.

however - while doing this djt with the brave bunch known as gop has willingly opened a pussy wound that anyone around the world can easily contaminate. i like to call it meddlin' with presidental blessin'. i'm not the only one who knows this opportunity and messes with the bombastic patriots - may be russia or china or mbs or antifa or me me me
column2: a tiny quarter pounder sitting on my bed.

column1: the whole qshow seems like a vile roleplay but instead it has become the heart of the propaganda operation that joseph goebbels would have died for. it is obvious that stuff like pizzagateâ„¢ was testing and groundwork for the 2016 election and since it proved to be very effective it is used still

the accompanying memes go way beyond the propaganda of nsdap. social media companies are just helpless with the fake content - there is no way they are going to risk their business by taking a real responsibility.

column2: â€œ what does sexual abuse feels like?â€ i will never find enough words and feelings to describe what it feels like but with all that i have seen it definitely does not feel like something that can be cured with
column4: get over it.â€ it does not feel like something that will justify my motherâ€™s discomfort when i mention it again and again. it does not feel like something where my guy friend can give me a blank look when i tell him i have gone through it. it does not feel like something that can be laughed off completely disregarding the years of trauma iâ€™ve gone through. it does not feel like something that will make me believe that no man will hurt me when the guy i trusted took away my sense of being alive away
column5: forever. it does not feel like something that i can move on from and love a guy. it does not feel like something that will not make me contemplate ending myself.  i cannot tell you what sexual abuse feels like but i can tell you a lot many things

column1: 133808;instagram;2018-11-27 05:48:50;FALSE;"wylie said that bannon's plans began to solidify in 2014
column2: when cambridge analytica consulted various republican campaigns and pacs ahead of the midterm elections. the company began to test and apply its psychographics by using facebook data to model individuals' personality types in order to understand how to influence them.

column1: documents show the john bolton super pac
column2: which promoted candidates supported by recently appointed white house national security adviser john bolton
column4: 700 in 2014 for ""behavioral microtargeting with psychographic messaging."" those services included strategies that broke individual voters into ""clusters"" based on what messages would resonate with them.

column1: wylie also said the company used focus groups and messaging trials in 2014 to test some of the concepts that became core themes of the trump campaign
column2: such as ""drain the swamp"" and imagery of walls. ""a lot of the narratives of the trump campaign were what we were testing in 2014

column1: he added that bannon directly presided over much of the company's initial research. ""everything that we were doing ultimately had to be passed up to bannon for approval
column3: who left the company in late 2014.

column2: i gathered my courage and told my story about a #metoo moment with richard branson. i knew i had proof of what had happened to me. but i had changed my computers 2 or 3 times since the incident and could not remember which hard drive i had placed it on. i was contacted by a uk based paper and told my story... they wanted proof
column3: all i had was images and they wanted the video. they released the story without the video and i was dragged over these internet streets as being a liar
column4: a 'failed"" backing vocalist trying to extort money from branson or trying to ""revive"" my career. i was then contacted by a reputable us based paper
column5: washington post and by then i had found the video
column6: i sent them the video proof
column8: and who said what immediately following the incident. i was asked by that paper
column9: not to give to any other outlet and they would run the story... needless to say
column10: i was contacted again by the wp and was told they would not be running the story after all. upon further research
column11: i learned that the washington post had given an award to branson earlier last year.

column2: i thought that the truth would prevail when asked about what happened to provide context and truth to my story by those who witnessed the incident. but
column3: one person said they would not comment
column4: another lied and said all had a good time and branson said that he did not do anything to make anyone feel uncomfortable.  i was flabbergasted and dumbfounded
column5: to say the least. i could not believe that these people
column6: who i was loyal to a fault for 11 years
column7: would just leave me hanging out to dry. these internet streets are brutal
column8: honey! i said that i would release the video
column10: that what happened to me was real.... and that i am not a liar!
